        mechanisms of the Software;
    (i) Share, publish, disclose, or make available any License Key to any
        unauthorized person or entity;
    (j) Use a single License Key on more Machines than permitted by Your
        License Tier;
    (k) Use the Software for benchmarking or comparative analysis intended for
