        other life-critical application);
    (o) Remove or circumvent the obfuscation, encryption, or code protection
        applied to the Software;
    (p) Redistribute the Software framework or library binary as a standalone
        component separate from Your compiled Application.

3.2 COMPETITIVE USE. You acknowledge and agree that You shall not use knowledge
